A variety of building types, sizes, tenures, affordability and distribution of a scale and intensity that supports the purpose of the zone;
A mix of medium and high-density housing;
Convenient access to active transport and public transport options;
Efficient, well integrated and strategic use of available development sites; and
Convenient access to a range of open spaces.

