Residential activities
Activity status: Permitted
Where:
The activity is located:
Above ground floor level;
At ground floor level along any street edge not identified as an active frontage;
At ground floor level along any street edge not identified as a non-residential activity frontage;
At ground floor level along any street edge not identified as requiring verandah coverage.
Activity status: Restricted Discretionary
Where:
Compliance with the requirements of MCZ-R12.1.a is not achieved.
Matters of discretion are:
The matters in MCZ-P4, MCZ-P6 and MCZ-P7;
The extent and effect of non-compliance with MCZ-S5 and MCZ-S6;
The extent to which the residential activity contributes to or detracts from the surrounding public space.
Notification status: An application for resource consent made in respect of rule MCZ-R12.2.a is precluded from being either publicly or limited notified.

